data.description: This property has something for everyone in the family to love!  Beautifully maintained home with original woodwork, stained glass windows, and meticulous details throughout! Large bedrooms with plenty of closet space. Convenient office located just off the kitchen. Gorgeous patio featuring an in ground pool, adorable cabana, and a great deal of space for entertaining.  Huge heated garage with a shop.  Newer high efficiency furnace, pellet stove, and lots of extras included. A personal oasis ready for a new owner. Must see before it's gone!
